	(text_box "Notes:\n1. R_gs_chg = 3.3MΩ\n2. Sense R = 0.035V / OCD1 current (Swappable) + PWR rating = 0.036V * OCD1 I \n3. OCDP resistor = 383k ±1% (180ms-90ms) (swappable)\n4. CBI connected to VSS for self-balancing\n5. Leave CBO floating \n6. C_ini = 1uF\n7. R_vdd = 1kΩ\n8. C_vdd = 1uF\n9. R_ini = 100Ω for balancing current of 38mA\n10. PRES = high (to exit HIBERNATE) (could add a switch to enter HIBERBATE during transit)\n11. CCFG connected to AVDD for 4S\n12. Double check if D2 should be more than 16V, like 21V instead"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
